## Follow functionality

The **Follow** functionality is related to the social activity posted on the [Timeline (VX)](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_timeline-vx-widget_.md) widget

You can add the follow button to user profiles or posts.

When following someone, any status updates posted by them will display in your newsfeed.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

### How to add follow button

To add follow button, you can use the [Action list (VX)](docs.getvoxel.io_article_action-list-vx-widget_.md) widget.

The widget provides two actions related to following

- **Follow post author**
- **Follow post**

**Follow post author** is typically used in user profiles, while the **Follow post** action is used to follow individual posts

### Displaying number of followers and following

**Author followers:**

Dynamic tags **➝** Author **➝** Followers

**Author following:**

Dynamic tags **➝** Author **➝** Following

**Post followers:**

Dynamic tags **➝** Post **➝** Followers
